                            <li>Draw the gradient vector at the point <m>(2,2)</m>.</li>
                            <li>Is the directional derivative at <m>(2,2)</m> in the <m>\vec i</m> direction positive, negative, or approximately zero?</li>
                            <li>Is the directional derivative at <m>(2,2)</m> in the <m>\vec i-\vec j</m> direction positive, negative, or approximately zero?</li>
